    <date day="11" month="May" year="2025"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This document deals with end-to-end cryptographically signed e-mail.
   It introduces a novel structure for signed e-mail that is designed to
   avoid creating any disturbance in legacy e-mail clients.  This
   "unobtrusive" signature structure removes disincentives for signing
   e-mail.</t>
    </abstract>
